      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "White Desert Blossom",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "Ah, \u003CPL\u003E!\r\nYou can always count on endemic\r\nlife to help you on your hunts! And\r\nif you complete my request, johoho,\r\nyou can count on them to help com-\r\nmunicate with your friends! Hop to\r\nit-to it and these stickers are yours!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rakna-Kadaki",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La fleur du d\u00E9sert",
        "Client": "Hojo le M. de la Guilde",
        "Description": "Ah, \u003CPL\u003E !\r\nTu peux toujours compter sur\r\nla Faune locale pour t\u0027aider !\r\nEt si tu t\u0027occupes de ma\r\nrequ\u00EAte, la Faune t\u0027aidera \u00E0\r\ncommuniquer avec tes amis !\r\nAu boulot si tu veux ces stickers !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rakna-Kadaki",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Fiore del deserto bianco",
        "Client": "Hojo il capo della Gilda",
        "Description": "Ehi, \u003CPL\u003E! La\r\nfauna endemica ti verr\u00E0 in\r\naiuto durante la caccia. E se\r\ncompleti la mia richiesta, ti\r\ndar\u00E0 una mano a comunicare con\r\ni tuoi amici, ohohoh! Su, al\r\nlavoro e gli adesivi sono tuoi!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rakna-Kadaki",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wei\u00DFe W\u00FCstenblume",
        "Client": "Gildenmeister Hojo",
        "Description": "Ah, \u003CPL\u003E! Auf der\r\nJagd helfen dir Einheimische\r\nWesen stets! Und wenn du meine\r\nAnfrage erf\u00FCllst, johoho,\r\nhelfen sie dir bei der Kommu-\r\nnikation mit Freunden! Auf,\r\nauf, hol dir diese Sticker!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rakna-Kadaki.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Flor blanca del desierto",
        "Client": "Hojo el maestro del gremio",
        "Description": "\u00A1Ah, \u003CPL\u003E!\r\nPuedes usar fauna local cuando\r\ncazas. Y si te encargas de mi\r\npetici\u00F3n, \u00A1tambi\u00E9n podr\u00E1s\r\nusarla cuando hables con tus\r\namigos, jo, jo, jo! \u00A1Compl\u00E9tala\r\ny las pegatinas son tuyas!",
        "Target": "Caza un Rakna-Kadaki",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
